title: United Kingdom Imports of Wickerwork & Basketwork
description: Imports of Wickerwork & Basketwork in the United Kingdom increased to 10.50 GBP Million in September from 8.11 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Wickerwork & Basketwork in the United Kingdom averaged 5.21 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 28.55 GBP Million in March of 2022 and a record low of 1.98 GBP Million in December of 2000. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Wickerwork & Basketwork.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
